{"builtWith":"0.15.15","comments":[{"LineComment":" ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━"},{"LineComment":"                                            // hydrogen // schema // sensation"},{"LineComment":" ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━"},{"LineComment":" | Pillar 15: Sensation — How embodied AI entities perceive environment and self."},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## PURPOSE"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | The Sensation pillar completes the perception loop for embodied agents."},{"LineComment":" | While the Haptic pillar models OUTPUT (what agents emit to humans via"},{"LineComment":" | vibration/audio), Sensation models INPUT (what agents perceive from"},{"LineComment":" | their environment and their own embodied state)."},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## ARCHITECTURAL RATIONALE"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | Without Sensation:"},{"LineComment":" |   - Agents can EXPRESS distress (red shift, contracted size, jitter)"},{"LineComment":" |   - But cannot MODEL WHY they are distressed"},{"LineComment":" |   - Agents have position but no SENSE of being in that position"},{"LineComment":" |   - Agents can collide but cannot FEEL the impact"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | With Sensation:"},{"LineComment":" |   - Agent knows: \"I am touching something cold, rough, giving way\""},{"LineComment":" |   - Agent knows: \"Space around me is crowded, light is dim, pressure high\""},{"LineComment":" |   - Agent can say: \"I am uncomfortable because ContactPressure > threshold"},{"LineComment":" |     AND SpatialFreedom < minimum\""},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## INTEGRATION WITH WORLDMODEL PROOFS"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | Every sensation input MUST have provenance (Integrity.lean):"},{"LineComment":" |   - No fabricated sensations (White Christmas attack vector blocked)"},{"LineComment":" |   - Sensation data wrapped in ProvenInput for trustworthy sourcing"},{"LineComment":" |   - Absence of expected sensation triggers alert (Affective.lean)"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## CATEGORIES"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | 1. Proprioceptive — Self-awareness (where am I, what shape, how moving)"},{"LineComment":" | 2. Contact — Touch/pressure (what am I touching, surface properties)"},{"LineComment":" | 3. Environment — Ambient conditions (light, noise, crowding, space)"},{"LineComment":" | 4. Force — Physics sensation (gravity, external forces, impact)"},{"LineComment":" | 5. Temporal — Time perception (subjective time, processing load)"},{"LineComment":" | 6. Social — Agent-to-agent awareness (proximity, attention, trust)"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## SUBMODULES"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | - Sensation/Proprioceptive.purs — JointAngle, Reach, Balance, etc."},{"LineComment":" | - Sensation/Contact.purs — ContactPressure, Friction, Compliance, etc."},{"LineComment":" | - Sensation/Environment.purs — AmbientLight, Crowding, etc."},{"LineComment":" | - Sensation/Force.purs — GravityVector, ExternalForce, Impact, etc."},{"LineComment":" | - Sensation/Temporal.purs — SubjectiveTime, ProcessingLoad, etc."},{"LineComment":" | - Sensation/Social.purs — NearestAgentDistance, TrustLevel, etc."},{"LineComment":" | - Sensation/Molecules.purs — BodyState, EnvironmentState, etc."},{"LineComment":" | - Sensation/Compounds.purs — Comfort, Distress, Flow, etc."},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## DEPENDENCIES"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | - Prelude"},{"LineComment":" | - Hydrogen.Schema.Geometry (Vec3 for vectors)"},{"LineComment":" | - Hydrogen.Schema.Dimension (units for distances, times)"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## DEPENDENTS"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | - WorldModel.Sensation.lean (provenance proofs)"},{"LineComment":" | - Affective.lean (sensation causes affective state)"},{"LineComment":" | - Agent embodiment systems"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────"},{"LineComment":" | REFERENCES"},{"LineComment":" | ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | - WorldModel/Affective.lean — Wellbeing attestation, drift detection"},{"LineComment":" | - WorldModel/Integrity.lean — Sensory integrity, ProvenInput"},{"LineComment":" | - WorldModel/Rights.lean — Spatial sovereignty, resource bounds"},{"LineComment":" | - SCHEMA.md Pillar 15 — Complete atom/molecule/compound specification"}],"decls":[],"exports":[],"foreign":[],"imports":[{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[94,1535],"start":[94,1]}},"moduleName":["Hydrogen","Schema","Sensation","Compounds"]},{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[88,1226],"start":[88,1]}},"moduleName":["Hydrogen","Schema","Sensation","Contact"]},{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[89,1174],"start":[89,1]}},"moduleName":["Hydrogen","Schema","Sensation","Environment"]},{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[90,1099],"start":[90,1]}},"moduleName":["Hydrogen","Schema","Sensation","Force"]},{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[93,1059],"start":[93,1]}},"moduleName":["Hydrogen","Schema","Sensation","Molecules"]},{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[87,975],"start":[87,1]}},"moduleName":["Hydrogen","Schema","Sensation","Proprioceptive"]},{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[92,994],"start":[92,1]}},"moduleName":["Hydrogen","Schema","Sensation","Social"]},{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[91,917],"start":[91,1]}},"moduleName":["Hydrogen","Schema","Sensation","Temporal"]},{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[94,1535],"start":[76,1]}},"moduleName":["Prim"]}],"moduleName":["Hydrogen","Schema","Sensation"],"modulePath":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Sensation.purs","reExports":{"Hydrogen.Schema.